    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《闯关游戏》是一款解密游戏,玩家需要使用鼠标来触发场景里面的机关道具,来帮助主角前往出口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏一共有40个关卡,每个关卡都会拥有不同的机制和道具以及不同的失败结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras/86fd3f70370b3c9746cc7ac01c2bd0af.avif?t=1747892058\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras_big/86fd3f70370b3c9746cc7ac01c2bd0af.avif?t=1747892058 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中也会有相应的提示告诉你如何通关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras/17bf2a5dad7419128f64072d011490a3.avif?t=1747892058\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras_big/17bf2a5dad7419128f64072d011490a3.avif?t=1747892058 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras/7f36357b52803f182b7fa78f4612f814.avif?t=1747892058\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245390/extras_big/7f36357b52803f182b7fa78f4612f814.avif?t=1747892058 width=800 height=456 /></span></p>",
